  inoremap  <Right>  <NOP>
  noremap   <Up>     <NOP>
  noremap   <Down>   <NOP>
  noremap   <Left>   <NOP>
  noremap   <Right>  <NOP>

  " When you've writen : (colon), press %% very fast and it'll write the current
  " file's directory
